E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Come on, baby, get up. Come on, let's go again. To the left. We're getting Arab money. Come on, baby. We're getting Arab money.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~来吧，宝贝，起来。来，再来一遍，左边。花着阿拉伯金银。来，宝贝。花着阿拉伯金银。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Shoot out the cables holding the tank up. She'll be easy to take when she drops to the ground.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~把坦克的吊绳打断，车落地就能轻松开走了。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~I guess that's me, bro. Enjoy the NOOSE tank.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~那就是我了，兄弟。祝你NOOSE坦克玩得开心。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Who gives a shit, player? Bring her back to the site.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~有什么差别吗，玩家？开回工地就是了。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~You're wrong. I've got needs. I've got feelings. I'll talk to you soon, my friend.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~你错了。我也有需求，我也有感情。晚点再说吧，朋友。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Shhh. My Dada is still here. I can try to slip off. Will you meet me?
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~嘘，我爸还在呢。等到机会就溜，你能来找我吗？

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Time to fucking party. They got the NOOSE tank on some air transport shit. Let's get her.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~该他妈狂欢了，NOOSE的坦克是空运过来的，把它抢过来。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Maybe you're right, I don't have the means.
~z~Luckily for us, this stuff is too 'serious' for Yusuf to be invited.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~还好，这个会太「正式」了，Yusuf不配参加。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Mind flying this thing, man? I nearly crashed into a water tower on my way here - scary shit.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~还是你来开吧，哥们？路上差点撞到水塔，太吓人了。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~She is arriving. Shit They're going to lock her up.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~就要到了，他妈的，车要被锁起来了。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~You got a sniper rifle. How you missing this shit?
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~这可是狙击枪啊，怎么会打不中呢？

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~I want it. Come on baby, you and me. Doing our tank thing. Just rolling like some Desert Storm niggas.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~就是想要。来吧，宝贝，咱俩一起，拿下这辆坦克。在路上复刻沙漠风暴行动。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~What is that chopper? I haven't seen one before. So powerful!
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~那是什么飞机？从来没见过，好牛逼啊！

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~They're airlifting the tank across town. Let's intercept the bitch.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~坦克正在城里空运，咱们把它截了。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~No doubt. I'll see you round, yeah.
~z~Let me tell you something, man. I know some disadvantaged, needy cats. You don't need shit.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，哥们，我跟你说，跟我弱小无助的伙计们比，你需要个屁。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Take the stick, big hitter. I can't be seen driving my own chopper.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~你来开吧，大佬。不能被人发现我在飞自己的飞机。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~We're getting Arab money. We're getting Arab money. Ho, ho, ho, ho! And again. Let's go.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~花着阿拉伯金银。花着阿拉伯金银。嚯，嚯，嚯，嚯！再来，一起唱。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Just don't have an army of LCPD trailing you back when you do. Clear those shitheads off.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~回来的时候别带着一屁股警察，把这帮傻逼干掉。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Up here, motherfucker! Shit. Stand back while I pick this thing up.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~在上面，妈个逼的！操，我要起吊了，你站远点。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Hey, look, I got to go, bro. I'll keep an eye out for shovels though.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，听着，我要走了，兄弟。有铲子的话，我帮你留意一下。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Transport has arrived for Mr Luis Lopez. Jump on board.
~z~What's the problem, man? Why ain't we got this already?
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~怎么回事，哥们？为啥还没到手？

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~He thinks I'm waiting for him in the lobby.
~z~Give it up, bro. Come on. Come on!
~z~Don't worry, man. I got these controls again.
~z~If they get to the police station, we're fucked.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~万一送到了警局，我们就完了。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Goodbye my friend. Thank you for everything.
~z~I'm thinking maybe you should start fetishizing some other piece of hardware, man, and just give up on the NOOSE tank.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~你还是倒腾别的玩意去吧，别惦记NOOSE的坦克了。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~I will text you in about one minute about the tank, okay?
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~待会儿我发短信跟你说坦克的事，好吗？

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~You must shoot out the tank supports. Then we will take her when she lands on the ground.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~你得把钩子打断，车落地了我们才能开走。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~I know! A tunnel! Ah, we'll burrow in there and have the motherfucker in no time.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~有了！地道！挖条隧道，马上就能拿下车子。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~The biggest. My name will go down in history.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~最大的楼。我以后会名垂青史。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~How your eyes, man? You play with yourself too much as a child?
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~你眼睛呢，哥们？小时候把自己玩瞎了？

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~I need you to shoot out the tank's suspension cables. You can then commandeer her on the ground.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~我要你把坦克的吊索打断，落地后就能开走了。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~What kind of fool would try to land that thing in Star Junction?
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~什么傻逼会把飞机降落在星汇广场？

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Thanks for everything, bro. You're a fucking diamond.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~太谢谢你了，兄弟。你真他妈行啊。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~We got to intercept this NOOSE tank. They're airlifting her across the city.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~他们在空运NOOSE坦克，我们去把它截下来。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, I don't doubt that, man. What did you want?
~z~Shit, man. Didn't get the NOOSE tank and we lost a chopper. I'm going to have to write this one down to experience.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，坦克车没拿到，直升机也没了。得吸取一下教训了。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Listen, are we going to do this or what? I'm on the fucking clock, man.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~拜托，正事到底还干不干了？我按钟头收费的，大哥。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~And may I say, madam, this is not a very appropriate way for a married woman to dress.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~不得不说，太太，你这打扮...对一个有夫之妇来说成何体统。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~I'm going to own this square. Get out my way.
~z~OH They gotta be filming something or some shit. Check the chopper.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~噢，这是要拍电影吗，小心直升机。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~I think you want to moderate your use of the word, bro. It's not fuckin' cool, alright?
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~说话还是要多注意点，兄弟。这他妈不好玩，好吧？

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, bro. But the cops are all over me.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~是，兄弟，但是条子都冲我来了。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Luis, I think I can give old papadap the slip. Meet me in Star Junction.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~Luis，我可以趁老爸不注意开溜。去星汇广场等我。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~This is ridiculous. You think that is all I have done?
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~别开玩笑了，我就那么不正经吗？

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~I knew how much you wanted to roll with me in that NOOSE tank. I know how disappointed you must be.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~我知道你很想一起坐装甲车兜风，现在一定很失望吧。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Shit, man, so am I. I wouldn't miss this for the world. Even if Poppa does hold the purse strings, so to speak.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，我也觉得。绝不能放过这个机会，哪怕可能被老爸掐住钱袋子。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Man, shit, that place is impenetrable. How will we get our tank now?
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~天，操了，那地方可进不去啊。这还怎么偷坦克？

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Oh, Poppa! What are you doing here?
~z~Okay then. Okay. I will move my tank party to another weekend. We'll have fun some other time. So long, friend.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~那好吧，庆祝会得改期了。到时候再玩吧，再见了，朋友。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Have you not seen the site? The foundations to our Empire?
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~没见过我的工地吗？没见过帝国的根基吗？

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~I told them many times father, this is a disrespectful way to dress. Do they listen to me? Oh no, never! And you, by the way-
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~跟他们讲了很多次了，爸，这么打扮有失体统。他们听吗？不，就没听过！还有你，先别走，

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~If only he gave me a few billion I could really call my own, then maybe I would grow up.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~要是他能给我个几十亿自己支配，我才算长大了吧。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~They took her in there, man. My baby's all alone. Will you go in there and save her from those animals?
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~他们进到警局里了，哥们。我的车就摆在那了。你能不能进去英雄救美？

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Chill, baby. Get into it. Feel it. Let's go!
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~别急，宝贝。代入进去，感受一下。来吧。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Mr. Lewis. Y'Allah, he is the greatest technical advisor in the whole city. And this is his wife, Jaundice.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~Lewis先生。天啊，他是自由城最好的技术顾问。然后，这位是他老婆，Jaundice。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Hey, man. What is it, money? Is it money you want? Here, here. Have it. But come on, let's go get this thing... Come on!
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，哥们，咋了，钱不够？嫌钱不够多吗？来，来，拿去。行了吧，去把它弄来吧...来吧！

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~What is that holding the tank? I must have one.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~吊着坦克的是啥？我得搞一架。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Glad you could make it out from your daddy's warm embrace.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，恭喜你逃出了你爹的「怀抱」。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~- Yo.~n~- Hey.~n~- Yes. And you know...we were just having a little creative meeting and things went a bit crazy and I somehow lost my pants.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~－哟。~n~－嘿。~n~－那什么...我们在开创意小会，聊得有点上头了，然后...裤子自己就掉了。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~moving swiftly on you will be proud of my plans. I want to show you for the Imperial Amir Towers.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~推进顺利的话，你会为我的计划骄傲的。我想给你看看Amir帝国塔。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Well, if we cannot have the NOOSE tank, at least no one else can either.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~就算我们没得手，别人也拿不着车了。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Your helicopter has arrived. Come on, homie. Let's go.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~你的直升机到了，上来吧，哥们儿。我们走。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~I knew how disgraceful you were, but I didn't realize quite how shameful you were.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~我知道你作风不正，但没想到你居然这么不知廉耻。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Welcome! Welcome, Poppa. This is my business associate... err err... Mr... uh..
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~欢迎！欢迎，老爸。这是我的生意伙伴...呃...什么来着...

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Before you think about stealing one, man, it's just an air crane. You can buy them real easy.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~你别急着动歪脑筋，哥们，那是空中起重机。有钱就能买到。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, bro, fuckin' devastated. Anyway, te veo, bro.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~是啊，兄弟。太他妈倒霉了。再见吧，兄弟。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~and No Pants" I think I don't need to read it.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~和底裤时，已经没有什么深究的必要了。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~I tell you, Poppa, magisterial doesn't do justice to it!
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~告诉你吧，老爸，「鬼斧神工」都不足以形容！

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, I don't think I can handle any more of that shit, partner.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~这种事你还是别来找我了，搭档。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Shit. We didn't get her in time. They're taking her down. My baby!
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~操，我们动作太慢了，他们跑了。我的车！

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~We can't let them get where they're going, man.
~z~Nothing wrong with me, homeboy. I am going to build the biggest fucking building in this fucking town.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~我没病，老兄。我他妈要造全自由城最大的楼。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~If you want it that badly, I'll give it a go. Keep your phone on, okay?
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~真的想要的话，我可以去。电话聊，好吗？

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Shhhh. Go and leave right now! And don't you dare come back without
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~嘘！滚，赶紧滚出去！再敢回来你就...

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~It's an aircrane, bro. Do me a favor, will you. Just fucking buy one, okay? No stealing.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~那是空中起重机。别麻烦我了，好吗？自己买一个好不好？别去偷了。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Get the last one and she drops!
~z~Well, I'm glad you learned from it, bro. I'll catch you round..
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~能吸取教训就好，兄弟。回头见。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Good thing you're in a motherfucking tank!
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~哈哈，幸好你小子开的是坦克！

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Of course. Of course. I mean, this is work, isn't it?
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~当然了，当然了。我说，这样算是工作吧？

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~This cannot be. I needed her so badly.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~怎么能这样。我真的很需要她。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~uh- uh- knocking...first.These people are a disgrace, Poppa. But I tell you,
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~呃...先...敲门！这帮人真是不要脸，老爸。我跟你说，

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Tell me about it! They think they can run your life. I'm old and ugly enough to take care of myself.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~还用你说！自以为能掌控孩子的人生。我已经够老够油了，可以照顾好自己。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~In fact, they are just going. Go, get out. You, Mr. Lewis, take your wife, Mrs. Lewis.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~实际上，他们刚要走。走，走，出去。你，Lewis先生，带着Lewis太太出去。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Come on. We can do this quick.
~z~Dada's meeting some bankers in the Exchange.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~爸爸在证交区和银行家开会。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Never! Impossible! Not when he sees everything I have achieved here in Liberty City.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~绝不！不可能！见过我在自由城的战果后就不可能。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~A coke habit? Maybe some venereal disease? Is that what you call an achievement?
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~毒瘾吗？说不定还有性病？这就是你的战果？

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~But you know, Poppa, I tell you are looking- you're looking- very well, in fact.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~其实吧，老爸，你今天气色...气色不错，真的。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Ugly? Yeah. Old? Sure. The 'taking care of yourself' bit, I don't know about that, bro.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~油？确实。老？的确。能照顾好自己？这我有点怀疑，兄弟。
~z~得从头再来了，哥们。不好意思。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~This is the best sniper money can buy. Come on.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~这是能买到的最好的狙了，拜托。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Nicely done. Now we just need the rest of the supports.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~干得好，打掉剩下的钩子就好了。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Well, I heard from a friend, that we can get some real hardware...bit like that chopper but better, partner. Better.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~呃，一个朋友说，又有搞真家伙的机会...跟秃鹰有点像，但是更猛，搭档。更猛。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~The tank. Shit, bro, it's kind of fucked.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~坦克？妈的，兄弟，坦克出问题了。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Poppa, you know, these people...They mean nothing to me.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~老爸，这些人...对我来说都不算啥。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Don't judge a book by its cover, Father. That's what you taught me.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~不能只看表面啊，爸。这你是教我的。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~You need a better zoom on that thing?
~z~There he is. That original desert storm bad boy.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~他来了，正宗的沙漠风暴恶霸。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Ummm. I don't know about that. Maybe.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~呃，我不太清楚，兄弟。应该是吧。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~I hope this is another Government Publicity Stunt.
~z~I will man. Going to have this shit customised. It's gonna be one opulent bad boy when I'm done.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~好的，哥们。我会拿去改装的。改装完就是豪车中的恶霸了。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Let's do it quick, partner. Come on.
~z~It's only a fucking cable. You want me to shoot?
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~就是根绳子罢了，要我来打吗？

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~I guess that's one way of looking at it, Bro. Later, Okay.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~这么一想倒也还行，兄弟。再见了。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Dammit. We didn't free her up in time, they're taking her in.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~我操，没及时打下来，他们到地方了。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~Fine. I wanted her so badly. Call me spoilt. Say what you like.
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~那好，我很想得到她。骂我巨婴吧，爱咋骂咋骂。

E2Y3AUD.original: ~z~What do you need a N.O.O.S.E tank for, man? What are you crime fighting now?
E2Y3AUD.translated: ~z~你要NOOSE的坦克干啥？打击犯罪吗？
